      "title_zh": "受美国政府指令影响，Anthropic 宣布停止所有用户对 Claude Fable 5 模型的访问权限",
      "title_orig": "As a result of a US government directive, we are suspending access to Claude Fable 5 for all users. You can continue to use all other Claude models. H...",
